                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">For solo only: if you do no damage at all, you lose 75% of the experience.  If you do 1 point, you lose 33%; if you do more than 50% damage, you get full experience.  It is believed that exp between those points scales proportionately.
<br />

<br />
This is not quite what SoE said back in their charm nerf patch message; however, it has been verified by several enchanters and confirmed here and on the cr board.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
