                                <td colspan="2"><hr /></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">DC = Charm rules.
<br />

<br />
Summoned pets will take 50% of the exp unless your group does at least 1 damage, in that case the pet will take 0% of the exp.
<br />

<br />
Charmed pets will take 75% of the exp unless your group does 1 damage, in that case the pet will take about 50% of the exp. The less damage the pet does in comparision to the group the less exp it takes to a minimum of about 33%.
<br />

<br />
Wether the exp is deducted from your split or the whole groups i have no idea.
<br />

<br />
oh, the charmed exp% are approx seeing as SoE likes to screw with things but its close to what it seems and they said a few months ago.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
