<br />
So for every DC pet that even touches a mob the group loses 33%? Ouch!  
<br />

<br />
Something in the back of my head keeps telling me (gotta get back on those meds!) that if the pet did 49% or less that they stole 0% of the exp.  But then again, those same voices keep telling me that DC pets started playing by differnt rules than regular charmed ones a while back too. Any truth to that?
