                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The above poster is correct however, I not sure this one is entirely correct:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Normal charms get 75% of the exp if they do all the dmg, if you do one point they get 33% and it slides from there based on pet vs group dmg. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
