                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">DC pets take <span style="font-weight: bold">zero exp</span> as long as group outdamages DC pet
<br />
-- otherwise DC pet takes 50% to 75%
<br />

<br />

<br />
Charmed pets (nonDC) always take some exp, but never more than 33%
<br />
(and you don't have to do any damage)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Animations require you to do at least 1 pt of damage or pet takes 75%
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
I'm going to a make seperate post from SOE to make everything clear
<br />
<a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=1784" target="_blank">http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=1784</a></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81508" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Nadia Nightengale</a> 65 Enchantress
