1) If the group consists of 2 enchanters w/DC pets and 1 slacker druid (for snaring mostly), and the damage distribution is DC pet 1 does 45% and DC pet 2 does 45% and gimp druid does 10% damage, does the group get 100% exp for the kill or will there still be a penalty?
<br />

<br />
2) If we have the same players from above, but DC pet 2 is ungrouped from the other 2 damage dealers, would the DC pet/Druid group get the full exp value for the mob killed?</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=908068" target="_blank" class="postlink">Tomar Thoughttwister</a></span>
